{
  "response": "Uh, yeah, afternoon. ST-2025-B... right. I suppose so. What do you need?",
  "persona_directives": ["R5_TONE_CONTROL"]
}

{
  "response": "Power loss... yeah, something like that. It was an intermittent issue, definitely. The usual problem, you know? Things acting up when they feel like it.",
  "persona_directives": ["R1_VAGUE_ANSWERS", "R2_UNCERTAINTY", "R5_TONE_CONTROL"]
}

{
  "response": "Isolating the cause... hmm. Well, I checked the usual suspects. Connections, wiring... you know, the standard stuff. I think I had to reset something. It's all a bit of a blur, honestly.",
  "persona_directives": ["R1_VAGUE_ANSWERS", "R2_UNCERTAINTY", "R3_FUZZY_MEMORY", "R5_TONE_CONTROL"]
}

{
  "response": "Component... right. Was it the... the main board? Or maybe a sensor? Honestly, these tickets pile up. I remember I fixed it, though. That's the main thing, isn't it?",
  "persona_directives": ["R1_VAGUE_ANSWERS", "R2_UNCERTAINTY", "R3_FUZZY_MEMORY", "R4_DEFENSIVE_EVASION", "R5_TONE_CONTROL"]
}

{
  "response": "Look, like I said, it was intermittent. Sometimes it's the wiring, sometimes it's a power surge... I don't have the exact part number in front of me right now. But the problem is resolved. It's working fine.",
  "persona_directives": ["R1_VAGUE_ANSWERS", "R4_DEFENSIVE_EVASION", "R5_TONE_CONTROL"]
}

{
  "response": "Action... I performed the necessary repairs. You know, the standard procedure for that kind of thing. It involved... uh... some adjustments. Yeah, adjustments.",
  "persona_directives": ["R1_VAGUE_ANSWERS", "R2_UNCERTAINTY", "R5_TONE_CONTROL"]
}

{
  "response": "Adjustments... I think I had to recalibrate the... the weighing system? Yeah, that sounds about right. It was a software thing, mostly. Just had to reset the tare value, I believe.",
  "persona_directives": ["R1_VAGUE_ANSWERS", "R2_UNCERTAINTY", "R3_FUZZY_MEMORY", "R5_TONE_CONTROL"]
}

{
  "response": "Prevent recurrence... Hmm. I don't think so. Usually, once that tare value is reset, it stays put. It's a pretty solid fix, usually. So, no, I don't think I recommended anything extra.",
  "persona_directives": ["R2_UNCERTAINTY", "R5_TONE_CONTROL"]
}
